<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Haggai on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/</link><description>Recent content in Haggai on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Haggai 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="haggai-chapter-1">Haggai Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="conversational-yahveh-covenant">Conversational Yahveh Covenant&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The
&lt;b>First Day, Sixth Month, Second Year of King Darius&lt;/b> &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>A Message from Yahveh to the Prophet Haggai &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>for Zerubbabel Ben-Shealtiel, Governor of Judah,&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>and for Joshua Ben-Jehozadak, the High Priest,&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="gods-call-to-rebuild-the-temple">God’s Call to Rebuild the Temple&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-bottom:0in; '>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Yahveh says, ‘These people are saying this is no time to be rebuilding Yahveh’s Temple.’”&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Haggai 2</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/chapter-02/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/haggai/chapter-02/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="haggai-chapter-2">Haggai Chapter 2&lt;/h2>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The
&lt;b>Twenty-First Day, Seventh Month&lt;/b>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>A Message from Yahveh to Haggai&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="the-new-temples-lesser-beauty">The New Temple’s Lesser Beauty&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in;margin-right:.5in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.5in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“Ask Zerubbabel, Joshua/&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Jeshua&lt;i> the high priest, and the remnant, &lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>‘How many of you saw this Temple in its former beauty? How does it look to you now? Doesn’t it seem like nothing in comparison? &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="verse verse-v4" id="v4">&lt;sup class="verse-num">4&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>But resolve to work because I’m with you. &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="verse verse-v5" id="v5">&lt;sup class="verse-num">5&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Like I promised when you came out of Egypt, my Spirit’s among you so you needn’t be afraid!’&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>